19:T44d,Internal evidence clearly describes ENFEED as a nasogastric feeding tube product family made from medical grade PVC for short-term enteral nutrition in critical care settings. External evidence confirms Meril Life Sciences manufactures medical devices including ENT products, but does not specifically verify the ENFEED brand or this exact product line. The brochure description is complete and clinically coherent, describing nasal tubes for enteral feeding with smooth insertion design. No SKU examples available to verify product variants. Classification as 'Nasogastric Tube' rather than generic 'Nasal Feeding Tube' is more clinically precise. The ENFEED brand name appears proprietary to Meril but lacks independent verification. Recommended for review to: (1) confirm ENFEED brand authenticity through official Meril catalogs, (2) verify whether this is standard NG tube or specialty variant, (3) obtain SKU data to understand product range (sizes, Fr gauges, lengths). Confidence moderate due to clear internal description but absence of external brand verification and product specifications.15:["$","$L18",null,{"product":{"product_name":"ENFEED Nasal Feeding Tubes","product_name_display":"ENFEED Nasal Feeding Tubes","sku_code":"MRL-ENF-013","product_family":"ENFEED Nasal Feeding Tubes","product_family_display":"ENFEED Nasal Feeding Tubes","slug":"enfeed-nasal-feeding-tubes","images":[{"id":"4e10593ff732","storage_path":"agile-ortho/products/69c3dee16be1486691088247/cc_cover_e7723106.jpg","original_filename":"critical_care_p4.jpg","content_type":"image/jpeg","size":282733,"uploaded_at":"2026-03-26T06:06:37.646006+00:00","source":"brochure_extraction"}],"status":"published","live_visible":true,"brochure_url":"","seo_meta_title":"ENFEED Nasal Feeding Tubes | ENFEED Enteral Feeding - MedDevice Pro Telangana","seo_meta_description":"ENFEED Nasal Feeding Tubes are premium medical grade PVC enteral feeding devices designed for short-term nasogastric nutrition and medicati